This directory contains the files needed to define the TABLES system.
These include:

tables.cl	master CL file; defines tasks within TABLES
tables.hd	master help database definition file for TABLES
tables.men	menu file for tasks in the TABLES package
tables.par	TABLES parameter file
mkpkg		IRAF mkpkg file to rebuild the TABLES package

and the applications directory containing:

    FITS input/output for images and tables
    STScI graphics task for images and tables
    table manipulation tools
